    java.io.Serializable

    public class ScheduleConflictException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException
    Created by NickNatali on 1/22/17. The ScheduleConflictException class refers to a runtime exception, that indicates that the client has attempted to introduce a conflict into a course schedule (overlapping courses).
